      <title>格陵兰人以 85% 多数反对特朗普加入美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/greenlanders-reject-trump-with-85-majority-against-joining-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格陵兰岛民众绝大多数反对脱离丹麦王国而加入美国，这对唐纳德·特朗普总统坚持格陵兰岛希望加入美国的决定造成了打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/greenlanders-reject-trump-with-85-majority-against-joining-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大央行将在关税酝酿之际缩减降息规模：决策指南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bank-of-canada-to-downsize-cuts-as-tariffs-brew-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行很可能在周三将利率下调四分之一个百分点，因为央行官员们正在分析美国关税将如何破坏加拿大经济的软着陆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bank-of-canada-to-downsize-cuts-as-tariffs-brew-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 18:59:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫称特朗普暂停拨款并非“全面”冻结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/white-house-says-no-across-the-board-funding-pause-amid-furor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的政府急忙澄清一份暂停联邦拨款、贷款和财政援助的备忘录，称白宫预算办公室的指示并非旨在“全面”冻结。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/white-house-says-no-across-the-board-funding-pause-amid-furor</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 18:43:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟和美国高级外交官讨论就乌克兰战争向俄罗斯施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/top-eu-us-diplomats-discuss-pressuring-russia-over-ukraine-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位了解电话交谈情况的欧盟官员透露，欧盟外交政策负责人卡娅·卡拉斯和美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥一致认为，有必要对俄罗斯施加最大压力，推动乌克兰实现公正、可持续的和平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/top-eu-us-diplomats-discuss-pressuring-russia-over-ukraine-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 18:21:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的交通部长人选已获参议院确认</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-s-transportation-secretary-pick-is-confirmed-by-senate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普选定的交通部长肖恩·达菲于周二顺利通过确认投票，这将使他能够执行特朗普针对铁路、汽车和航空业的议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-s-transportation-secretary-pick-is-confirmed-by-senate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 18:02:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大外长弗里兰称特朗普威胁盟友向中国发出信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-is-threatening-allies-to-send-signal-to-china-canada-s-freeland-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正在角逐贾斯汀·特鲁多总理职位的加拿大政治家克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰 (Chrystia Freeland) 表示，加拿大可以与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的政府合作，重塑全球贸易并削弱中国在供应链中的主导地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-is-threatening-allies-to-send-signal-to-china-canada-s-freeland-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 17:37:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普政府因美国停止拨款遭非营利组织起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-administration-sued-over-omb-halt-to-federal-grants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府因一项暂停支付大范围联邦补助、贷款和援助的新计划而面临诉讼，此举可能影响全国数十亿美元的资金流动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-administration-sued-over-omb-halt-to-federal-grants</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 17:17:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国考虑让 Netflix 用户支付许可费以资助 BBC</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/uk-considers-making-netflix-users-pay-license-fee-to-fund-bbc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国正考虑让仅使用 Netflix 和 Disney 等流媒体服务的家庭支付 BBC 许可费，这是其对这家公共服务广播公司的资金筹集方式进行现代化改造计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/uk-considers-making-netflix-users-pay-license-fee-to-fund-bbc</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 16:30:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布蒂吉格和麦克莫罗争夺密歇根州参议员席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/buttigieg-said-to-weigh-bid-for-senate-after-peters-bows-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在参议员加里·彼得斯宣布不再竞选连任后，皮特·布蒂吉格和州参议员马洛里·麦克莫罗正在考虑是否竞选密歇根州参议员席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/buttigieg-said-to-weigh-bid-for-senate-after-peters-bows-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 15:54:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗伯特·肯尼迪在参议院听证会前表示他并不反对疫苗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/rfk-jr-walks-back-vaccine-rhetoric-before-hhs-senate-hearings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗伯特·F·肯尼迪 (Robert F. Kennedy Jr.) 是唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 总统提名的美国卫生与公众服务部部长，他本周将告诉参议员，他并不“反对疫苗或反对产业”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/rfk-jr-walks-back-vaccine-rhetoric-before-hhs-senate-hearings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
